Package pulse.problem.schemes.solvers

Contains various finite-difference solvers for the different problem statements available. Each solver is tailored to a specific problem statement and the solution is highly hard-coded.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Solver<T extends Problem>
    A solver interface which provides the capability to use the solve method on a Problem.
